This program is to make slab structure where surface plane appears.
The crystal structural format comes from the input in VASP software.

*Usage: ./build_slab.ver9.3 POSCAR VECTOR VACUUM_H LAYERS_N EXPAND_X_TIMES EXPAND_Y_TIMES OPT_SQRT(3) 
Input:
	POSCAR: POSCAR filename of unit cell structure
	VECTOR: specify the plane type; (1 0 0) = 1, (1 1 0) = 2, (1 1 1) = 3
	VACUUM_H: specify the vacuum length (Angstrom)
	LAYERS_N: specify the number of layers
	EXPAND_X_TIMES, EXPAND_Y_TIMES: specify the integer number for expansion parameters to x and y axis
	OPT_SQRT(3): convert to sqrt(3)Xsqrt(3)R30degree for surface reconstruction; on: 1, off: 0

Output:
	POSCAR.out: POSCAR file to cleave assigned plane
	NOTE) Fix 2 bottom layers in final structure for running VASP program		


